This six-week course packs a lot of information in a few lectures. The syllabus could be a template for a complete university graduate coursework. The lectures and lecturers from University of Zurich are great. I listen to each lecture at least three times. A member of the teaching staff, Isabel Meraner, is extremely knowledgeable and quickly responds to all questions or comments. I would be happy to take another course from these developers from University of Zurich.
Sehr gut strukturierter Kurs! Man lernt viele aktuelle Methoden, Begriffe und Tools kennen, die man in dne unterschiedlichsten Projekten anwenden kann! Ein zeitnaher Kurs zu einem spannenden Thema!
